text: Anopyxis klaineana is a species of plant in the Rhizophoraceae family. It is found in Cameroon, the Republic of the Congo, Ivory Coast, Ethiopia, Ghana, Liberia, Nigeria, Sierra Leone, and Sudan. ==References== Category:Rhizophoraceae Category:Vulnerable plants Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot
title: Anopyxis klaineana
